### Do you offer payroll and employment services?

No, we don't. However, if you use an **Employer of Record (EoR)** third-party service, such as [Remote](https://remote.com), you can reimburse their invoices through your Collective. Bear in mind that an EoR service has to be contracted outside of Open Collective Europe through an incorporated entity. Please make sure to review their website, pricing, and documentation. Feel free to contact us if your Collective requires our support on the matter.

{% hint style="danger" %}
Please note that Open Collective Europe cannot contract any EoR service on behalf of your Collective.
